Mrs Jacqueline Newman.
A loving wife, mother and grandmother who passed away on 1 March 2009.
She had the highest admiration and respect for Inner Temple and Temple Church."ž
šTHIS MEMORIAL OF REV. HENRY SUMMERHAYES
DIRECTOR OF ST. MICHAEL'S SCHOOL. 1913-1928
DEDICATED BY
DR. MARGARET HUSTLER HEADMISTRESS 1989-1996
ON 28th SEPTEMBER 1997

IN MEMORY OF THE REV HENRY SUMMERHAYES DIRECTOR 1913-1928

IN MEMORY OF
ST. MICHAEL'S SCHOOL, LIMPSFIELD 1850-1996
REMEMBERED BY
PUPILS, STAFF, GOVERNORS AND PARENTS"▌
